2026-03-22 19:10:49,209 - INFO - AI Response: Bilkul sahi sawal hai! Article 21 ka daayra bahut bada hai aur iski vyakhya courts ne samay-samay par badhayi hai.

Iske kuch pramukh hisse aur aapko milne wali azadiyan is prakar hain:

1.  Samman ke Saath Jeene ka Adhikar (Right to Live with Human Dignity): Ismein sirf zinda rehna hi nahi, balki ek accha, sammanjanak aur arthpurn jeevan jeena shamil hai.
2.  Vyaktigat Azadi (Personal Liberty): Ismein aapko apni marzi se apni zindagi jeene ki azadi shamil hai, jaise yatra karna, apni pasand ka kaam karna, jab tak aap kisi kanoon ka ullanghan na karein.
3.  Swachh Paryavaran ka Adhikar (Right to Clean Environment): Aapko swachh hawa aur paani mein rehne ka adhikar hai.
4.  Swasthya ka Adhikar (Right to Health): Aapko acchi chikitsa suvidhayein milne ka adhikar hai.
5.  Shiksha ka Adhikar (Right to Education): 6 se 14 saal ke bachchon ke liye muft aur anivarya shiksha ka adhikar (Article 21A ke tahat bhi hai, jo Article 21 se hi nikla hai).
6.  Nijta ka Adhikar (Right to Privacy): Aapko apni niji jaankari aur jeevan mein dakhalandazi se bachne ka adhikar hai.
7.  Roji-roti ka Adhikar (Right to Livelihood): Aapko jeevan yapan ke liye sahi saadhan kamane ka adhikar hai.
8.  Jald Sunwai ka Adhikar (Right to Speedy Trial): Yadi aap par koi mamla hai, toh uski sunwai jald se jald hone ka adhikar.

Toh, Article 21 aapko ek sammanjanak, azad aur surakshit jeevan jeene ki buniyadi garantee deta hai.
