Bharat mein Article 21 kehta hai ki "Kisi bhi vyakti ko uske pran aur dhaarik swatantrata se, kanoon dwara sthapit prakriya ke alawa, vanchit nahi kiya jayega."

Seedhe shabdon mein, iska matlab hai ki aapko jeene ka aur apni marzi se apni zindagi guzarne ka adhikar hai, jab tak aap kanoon ka palan kar rahe hain.

Iske mukhya hisse hain:

1.  Jeene ka Adhikar (Right to Life): Iska matlab sirf saans lena nahi hai, balki izzat aur garima ke saath jeena. Ismein shamil hain:
       Shudh hawa aur paani ka adhikar.
       Swasthya ka adhikar.
       Ek achhe vaatavaran mein rehne ka adhikar.
       Bhojan ka adhikar.
       Aashray ka adhikar (ghar ka).
       Shiksha ka adhikar.

2.  Vyaktigat Swatantrata ka Adhikar (Right to Personal Liberty): Iska matlab hai ki aapko manmani giraftari ya kaid se bachne ka adhikar hai, aur ismein kai aur cheezein bhi shamil hain jaise:
       Nijta ka adhikar (Right to Privacy).
       Videsh yatra ka adhikar.
       Tej sunwai ka adhikar (Right to speedy trial).

Yeh Article bahut vyapak hai aur Supreme Court ne samay-samay par ismein aur bhi adhikar shamil kiye hain jo ek insaan ki garima purn jeevan ke liye zaroori hain.
