2026-03-22 19:13:19,532 - INFO - AI Response: Achha sawal hai!

Bharat mein "Fundamental Rights" (mool adhikar) wo buniyadi adhikar hain jo hamare samvidhan ne har nagarik ko diye hain. Ye isliye "fundamental" hain kyunki ye aapke jeene aur garima ke saath rehne ke liye bahut zaroori hain. Koi bhi sarkar ya sanstha in adhikaron ko aapse asaani se nahi chheen sakti.

Ye mool adhikar samvidhan ke Part III mein diye gaye hain aur unmein se kuch pramukh hain:

1.  Samanta ka Adhikar (Right to Equality): Kanoon ke samne sab barabar hain aur kisi ke saath dharm, jaati, ling, ya janm sthan ke aadhar par bhedbhav nahi hoga. (Article 14-18)
2.  Swatantrata ka Adhikar (Right to Freedom): Ismein bolne ki azadi, ikattha hone ki azadi, ghoomne ki azadi, aur vyavsay karne ki azadi shamil hai. (Article 19-22)
       Article 21 (Pran aur Dhaarik Swatantrata ka Adhikar) jiske baare mein humne abhi baat ki, woh bhi isi mein aata hai.
3.  Shoshan ke Viruddh Adhikar (Right Against Exploitation): Ismein bal shram (zabardasti kaam karana) aur manav taskari (insaanon ki kharid-firokht) par rok lagayi gayi hai. (Article 23-24)
4.  Dharmik Swatantrata ka Adhikar (Right to Freedom of Religion): Har vyakti ko apni marzi se kisi bhi dharm ko manne, uska palan karne aur prachar karne ki azadi hai. (Article 25-28)
5.  Sanskriti aur Shiksha Sambandhi Adhikar (Cultural and Educational Rights): Alpsankhyak samudayon ko apni sanskriti aur bhasha ko bachane aur shiksha sansthan sthapit karne ka adhikar hai. (Article 29-30)
6.  Sanvaidhanik Upcharon ka Adhikar (Right to Constitutional Remedies): Agar aapke kisi mool adhikar ka ullanghan hota hai, toh aap is adhikar ke तहत seedhe Supreme Court ya High Court ja sakte hain. Ise Baba Saheb Ambedkar ne 'Samvidhan ki Aatma aur Hridaya' kaha tha. (Article 32)

Kya aap kisi khaas mool adhikar ke baare mein janana chahte hain ya aapko lagta hai ki aapke kisi adhikar ka ullanghan ho raha hai?
